msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8d2e37400a05a928f8f62ca42c985a524c8b62","tid":2090164,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536efd944cdf7ea42b51c5c07c949b42bb8ab30f","tid":2090164,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78ed2063a05a6ad43ed369cf41f996cc48a1d52c","tid":2090164,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"借個位，BNO平權正視聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑色五毛分化警告，大量五毛正在用藍絲有BNO、走人對唔住97後割97後等風向進行分化</span></span></strong>，大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家比人拉過/有小朋友（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）的話就應該即刻走</span></span></strong>，其他人亦應該起碼做好隨時走既準備，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港抗爭運動已經由本土抗爭升級為準國際戰爭， 我們能做的十分有限。 相反大家離開或準備好隨時可以離開，則美國及其盟友可以隨時採取行動，對香港進行制裁，令香港達至零經濟活動，攬炒香港經濟， 甚至日後作出軍事行動亦無需擔心誤傷香港人。</span></span></strong> 而且大家亦可用移民理由提取所有資產及強積金進一步<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊香港的財政儲備</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而且多人走亦可以起到掩護最需要走既手足，救奶左野手足係目前最重要既事。<br />\n<br />\n2.大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無需擔心藍絲以及黑警移民英國</span></span></strong>，藍絲得兩種a.垃圾b.收成期，a.涯唔到六年移民監b.揾錢唔捨得走/走要承受巨大損失<br />\n<br />\n重點：大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不應該反對平權或推到現階段設立篩選，因為這樣會妨礙奶左野手足逃難</span></span></strong>。反而，大家應該在藍絲移民英國後再篤灰。大家，要記住，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">篤灰係一把藍絲頭上既利劍，一日未入籍一日都嚮度，我就係要佢地嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">相反藍絲黑警，反而大家更應該想辦法推動取消侵犯人權者如689、777、鳩融居英權，因為他們可以一直不居英，不受英國審判，而定居歐洲。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望樓主可以pin，一齊擊退五毛</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"51899954f05154b848c6982d0bd023ca1e25ca63","tid":2090164,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dde04fe746ce87395e3b118bbd0a57f1202492c0","tid":2090164,"uid":55924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"我等緊個藍屍同事去美國旅行舉報佢😆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"會去fbi或者homeland <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64ba5f407614e04f2772d118e895fff5cb28c4b","tid":2090164,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edee5b8dcb746cdc64acba0718403c431555047f","tid":2090164,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51899954f05154b848c6982d0bd023ca1e25ca63","tid":2090164,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dde04fe746ce87395e3b118bbd0a57f1202492c0","tid":2090164,"uid":55924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"我等緊個藍屍同事去美國旅行舉報佢😆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"會去fbi或者homeland <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\